1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:22,000
(Watch on www.kisskh.xyz Support Admin)

2
00:00:21,840 --> 00:00:23,260
♪Wandering alone♪

3
00:00:23,260 --> 00:00:25,540
♪Walking far by dusk-lit streets♪

4
00:00:25,540 --> 00:00:27,430
♪Your eyes are as cold as clouds♪

5
00:00:27,430 --> 00:00:28,970
♪Faintly coming into view♪

6
00:00:28,970 --> 00:00:30,360
♪The city lights♪

7
00:00:30,360 --> 00:00:32,630
♪Lit up that single moment♪

8
00:00:32,630 --> 00:00:36,140
♪I can't hide or stop missing you♪

9
00:00:36,140 --> 00:00:37,640
♪I can't forget those moments♪

10
00:00:37,640 --> 00:00:39,280
♪Losing you♪

11
00:00:39,610 --> 00:00:41,320
♪Like the seasons in my memory♪

12
00:00:41,320 --> 00:00:43,290
♪Without winter♪

13
00:00:43,290 --> 00:00:44,920
♪Walking down the long, dark street♪

14
00:00:44,920 --> 00:00:46,460
♪Snow will never fall again♪

15
00:00:46,460 --> 00:00:48,200
♪Our old story was torn♪

16
00:00:48,200 --> 00:00:50,610
♪Into scattered pieces♪

17
00:00:50,610 --> 00:00:53,430
♪Replaying every single scene♪

18
00:00:53,430 --> 00:00:55,980
♪After you left♪

19
00:00:57,530 --> 00:01:00,510
♪As if our documentary♪

20
00:01:00,510 --> 00:01:03,120
♪Lost winter♪

21
00:01:04,770 --> 00:01:07,180
♪The breeze speaks of good times♪

22
00:01:07,180 --> 00:01:11,080
♪Pure white devotion♪

23
00:01:11,680 --> 00:01:13,990
♪Send out a letter♪

24
00:01:14,300 --> 00:01:17,780
♪Carrying my longing♪

25
00:01:17,780 --> 00:01:20,980
=The Double Game=

26
00:01:21,020 --> 00:01:23,940
=Episode 5=

27
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:42,450
♪This door♪

28
00:01:42,850 --> 00:01:47,600
♪Lets in the sky outside♪

29
00:01:47,760 --> 00:01:48,600
Zhi'er,

30
00:01:48,950 --> 00:01:50,200
Tingyu's still waiting at home.

31
00:01:51,640 --> 00:01:54,450
♪Than how you just greeted me♪

32
00:01:54,900 --> 00:01:56,270
♪I know now♪

33
00:01:56,600 --> 00:02:00,990
♪What the chill in my body means♪

34
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:01,840
Lu Tingyu

35
00:02:02,430 --> 00:02:04,760
could be with some influencer now.

36
00:02:04,900 --> 00:02:08,320
♪My heart still beats so naively♪

37
00:02:08,750 --> 00:02:09,680
They can be unfaithful,

38
00:02:10,150 --> 00:02:10,990
but that doesn't mean

39
00:02:11,346 --> 00:02:12,360
we have to cross the line.

40
00:02:12,370 --> 00:02:15,690
♪A joy that needs no brave pretense♪

41
00:02:16,710 --> 00:02:17,750
What I hate most is

42
00:02:18,750 --> 00:02:20,150
the mistress and the cheater.

43
00:02:22,330 --> 00:02:24,650
♪Maybe you just passed by♪

44
00:02:24,650 --> 00:02:28,230
♪The tears in my eyes♪

45
00:02:28,940 --> 00:02:30,820
♪You looked like you had nothing to say♪

46
00:02:30,840 --> 00:02:31,710
You act so aloof.

47
00:02:31,720 --> 00:02:33,230
♪Then got so good at being cold♪

48
00:02:33,230 --> 00:02:36,070
♪That's why a smile feels so precious♪

49
00:02:36,280 --> 00:02:38,370
♪Maybe you just passed by♪

50
00:02:38,520 --> 00:02:42,850
♪The tears burned into my heart♪

51
00:02:43,230 --> 00:02:45,520
♪Let's say silence was just for show♪

52
00:02:45,520 --> 00:02:50,190
♪Even if I've grown another year♪

53
00:03:16,470 --> 00:03:18,080
(What is this guy trying to do?)

54
00:03:18,680 --> 00:03:19,630
(So fickle.)

55
00:03:20,030 --> 00:03:21,280
(Is he testing me)

56
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:22,680
(or...)

57
00:03:30,430 --> 00:03:31,270
Sis.

58
00:03:31,960 --> 00:03:32,800
Sis.

59
00:03:34,080 --> 00:03:35,370
Sis, something's wrong.

60
00:03:35,400 --> 00:03:36,310
Keep it down.

61
00:03:36,870 --> 00:03:38,150
You want Jianchuan to find out

62
00:03:38,310 --> 00:03:39,400
what trouble you cause?

63
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:41,840
You just got 50 million in funding.

64
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:43,840
I even covered it from my private fund.

65
00:03:44,150 --> 00:03:45,470
Xu Wangzu,

66
00:03:45,636 --> 00:03:47,000
how many messes have I cleaned up?

67
00:03:47,190 --> 00:03:48,280
This time, it's not just me.

68
00:03:48,430 --> 00:03:49,310
It's both of us.

69
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:53,520
About the Lianxin Island funding,

70
00:03:54,150 --> 00:03:55,840
a big overseas investor pulled out.

71
00:03:56,240 --> 00:03:57,360
Some small investors heard

72
00:03:57,960 --> 00:03:58,960
and started pulling out.

73
00:03:59,800 --> 00:04:00,960
They pulled their money.

74
00:04:01,190 --> 00:04:02,083
Why are you panicking?

75
00:04:02,190 --> 00:04:03,470
How can I not panic?

76
00:04:04,150 --> 00:04:06,120
Lu Tingxiao just killed my sweet deal.

77
00:04:06,590 --> 00:04:07,870
If the funding goes wrong too,

78
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:10,080
do you think we can go back there?

79
00:04:13,710 --> 00:04:14,550
Sis,

80
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:16,190
you must save me.

81
00:04:17,390 --> 00:04:18,270
Calm down.

82
00:04:18,493 --> 00:04:19,693
It's not the end of the world.

83
00:04:21,510 --> 00:04:23,720
Pulling funding happens all the time.

84
00:04:23,920 --> 00:04:25,750
Besides, this isn't on us.

85
00:04:28,870 --> 00:04:29,870
Actually,

86
00:04:31,270 --> 00:04:32,430
this could be our chance.

87
00:04:33,510 --> 00:04:34,350
Our chance?

88
00:04:35,000 --> 00:04:35,840
Do you have a plan?

89
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:39,920
I'll invite the execs over.

90
00:04:40,240 --> 00:04:41,080
Right now,

91
00:04:41,240 --> 00:04:42,830
go tip off those small investors

92
00:04:43,920 --> 00:04:45,310
and let them make a real scene.

93
00:04:46,310 --> 00:04:48,070
Isn't Lu Tingxiao so capable?

94
00:04:48,430 --> 00:04:50,510
Isn't he all fired up in his new role?

95
00:04:51,480 --> 00:04:53,600
Then I'll send this mess his way

96
00:04:54,120 --> 00:04:56,310
and make the fire burn even hotter.

97
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:59,240
Let's see how the new CEO fixes it.

98
00:05:05,830 --> 00:05:06,830
Things are lively today.

99
00:05:15,006 --> 00:05:16,172
Don't forget why you're here.

100
00:05:18,240 --> 00:05:19,390
Call Mr. Lu out here.

101
00:05:19,600 --> 00:05:21,160
He owes us an answer today.

102
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:24,510
What brings you all here?

103
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:25,640
Ms. Xu,

104
00:05:26,040 --> 00:05:27,360
we heard

105
00:05:27,630 --> 00:05:29,720
that the Lianxin Island project
was a scam.

106
00:05:30,070 --> 00:05:32,120
Even Xiao Ting pulled overseas funds.

107
00:05:32,450 --> 00:05:33,445
Not a cent of our money

108
00:05:33,456 --> 00:05:34,720
can be missing, right?

109
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:36,800
Pay it back with interest today.

110
00:05:37,390 --> 00:05:38,230
If you don't,

111
00:05:38,950 --> 00:05:40,240
we're not leaving today.

112
00:05:41,000 --> 00:05:42,160
Is that what's going on?

113
00:05:43,310 --> 00:05:44,240
Too bad.

114
00:05:44,630 --> 00:05:46,800
I no longer handle financing.

115
00:05:47,270 --> 00:05:48,950
The new CEO is in charge now.

116
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:50,560
Tingxiao,

117
00:05:51,390 --> 00:05:52,680
why don't you explain it?

118
00:05:59,000 --> 00:05:59,840
You?

119
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:02,070
You still owe me
for hitting me last time.

120
00:06:02,600 --> 00:06:03,440
Perfect timing.

121
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:05,120
Let's settle old and new scores today.

122
00:06:05,510 --> 00:06:06,589
Return our investment money

123
00:06:06,600 --> 00:06:07,750
with interest.

124
00:06:07,920 --> 00:06:08,830
- Yeah.
- Return it.

125
00:06:08,920 --> 00:06:09,770
Return it.

126
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:10,700
What's all this noise?

127
00:06:11,315 --> 00:06:12,494
- Chairman Lu.
- Chairman Lu.

128
00:06:12,505 --> 00:06:13,330
What's going on here?

129
00:06:14,593 --> 00:06:15,600
This is the Lu residence.

130
00:06:16,270 --> 00:06:17,920
Who said you could cause trouble here?

131
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:19,520
Chairman Lu,

132
00:06:19,750 --> 00:06:21,480
we're not here to cause trouble.

133
00:06:21,830 --> 00:06:22,670
But you should know

134
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:24,360
the project is tied to a scam.

135
00:06:24,680 --> 00:06:26,270
You're leaving us investors no way out.

136
00:06:26,630 --> 00:06:27,480
Today,

137
00:06:27,680 --> 00:06:28,520
you have to pay

138
00:06:28,750 --> 00:06:29,630
the money back.

139
00:06:29,830 --> 00:06:31,560
- Pay us back!
- Now, hurry!

140
00:06:31,830 --> 00:06:32,670
Everyone,

141
00:06:34,040 --> 00:06:35,040
let me make it clear.

142
00:06:35,950 --> 00:06:38,390
The Lianxin Island project is lawful.

143
00:06:38,830 --> 00:06:39,670
The so-called fraud

144
00:06:40,120 --> 00:06:41,750
is pure nonsense.

145
00:06:42,240 --> 00:06:43,600
Even Xiao Ting, an expert abroad,

146
00:06:44,070 --> 00:06:44,920
no longer trusts you.

147
00:06:45,190 --> 00:06:46,160
Stop fooling us.

148
00:06:47,040 --> 00:06:47,920
Today, if Luzhou Group

149
00:06:48,070 --> 00:06:49,630
can't give us an answer,

150
00:06:50,510 --> 00:06:52,000
we'll take legal action.

151
00:06:52,630 --> 00:06:53,470
Dad,

152
00:06:54,000 --> 00:06:54,840
I'll handle this.

153
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:57,960
Tingxiao,

154
00:06:59,120 --> 00:07:00,000
what will you do?

155
00:07:01,950 --> 00:07:02,830
Please stay calm.

156
00:07:03,630 --> 00:07:05,120
Just now, I contacted

157
00:07:05,600 --> 00:07:07,120
Mr. Xiao Ting for Luzhou Group.

158
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:08,920
He sent me a reply email.

159
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:17,830
Mr. Xiao Ting said

160
00:07:18,310 --> 00:07:20,000
someone misused the funds,

161
00:07:24,430 --> 00:07:26,160
so he's lost confidence in us.

162
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:27,950
Mr. Xiao Ting also said

163
00:07:28,510 --> 00:07:30,000
that if he sees our sincerity,

164
00:07:30,480 --> 00:07:31,800
he'll keep investing.

165
00:07:32,720 --> 00:07:33,750
Dad, look.

166
00:07:43,120 --> 00:07:43,960
I hereby announce

167
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:45,190
that from now on,

168
00:07:46,360 --> 00:07:48,600
Xu Shulin

169
00:07:48,950 --> 00:07:49,800
and Xu Wangzu

170
00:07:50,510 --> 00:07:52,360
are removed from all roles
at Luzhou Group.

171
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:54,190
All related businesses,

172
00:07:54,479 --> 00:07:55,925
including the Lianxin Island project,

173
00:07:56,270 --> 00:07:58,190
will be handed to the CEO
of Luzhou Group,

174
00:07:59,720 --> 00:08:00,920
Lu Tingxiao.

175
00:08:02,240 --> 00:08:03,080
Jianchuan.

176
00:08:07,830 --> 00:08:08,783
Everyone, please leave.

177
00:08:09,360 --> 00:08:11,630
As CEO of Luzhou Group, I promise

178
00:08:12,360 --> 00:08:14,160
I'll give you a fair answer.

179
00:08:16,390 --> 00:08:17,230
Mom.

180
00:08:19,290 --> 00:08:20,130
What?

181
00:08:20,160 --> 00:08:21,600
We can't leave without money.

182
00:08:21,950 --> 00:08:22,790
Know when to stop.

183
00:08:26,040 --> 00:08:26,880
Let's go.

184
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:46,280
Bai,

185
00:08:46,410 --> 00:08:47,412
how did you get involved

186
00:08:47,423 --> 00:08:48,600
in the fundraising scheme?

187
00:08:49,840 --> 00:08:50,700
Someone asked me

188
00:08:50,720 --> 00:08:51,633
to handle investments.

189
00:08:52,750 --> 00:08:53,766
Who's the boss behind it?

190
00:08:55,360 --> 00:08:56,200
Don't ask.

191
00:08:56,440 --> 00:08:57,280
It's for your good.

192
00:08:58,240 --> 00:08:59,080
Okay.

193
00:08:59,510 --> 00:09:00,440
How did you get mixed up

194
00:09:00,630 --> 00:09:01,510
with Fei Yifan?

195
00:09:03,270 --> 00:09:04,110
We invested together,

196
00:09:04,480 --> 00:09:06,200
so we got to know each other.

197
00:09:07,240 --> 00:09:09,120
Last time, I checked his pool hall.

198
00:09:09,390 --> 00:09:10,230
I later found out

199
00:09:10,720 --> 00:09:11,560
those honey traps

200
00:09:11,600 --> 00:09:13,000
were all set up by his partner,

201
00:09:13,320 --> 00:09:14,360
not his idea.

202
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:16,040
That kid

203
00:09:16,440 --> 00:09:17,320
has a bit of a temper,

204
00:09:17,680 --> 00:09:18,593
but he's not a bad guy.

205
00:09:19,320 --> 00:09:22,000
The pool hall folded. Money ran out.

206
00:09:22,240 --> 00:09:24,000
So, he came to recover his funds.

207
00:09:25,910 --> 00:09:26,750
I'll verify it.

208
00:09:27,120 --> 00:09:27,960
If it's true,

209
00:09:28,240 --> 00:09:29,150
I'll clear his name.

210
00:09:30,320 --> 00:09:31,750
Of all the kids from our orphanage,

211
00:09:31,959 --> 00:09:33,000
you are the most stubborn.

212
00:09:36,320 --> 00:09:37,160
Still,

213
00:09:37,600 --> 00:09:38,510
why are you here?

214
00:09:42,440 --> 00:09:43,510
It's a long story.

215
00:09:44,750 --> 00:09:45,670
In short,

216
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:47,840
I'm undercover.

217
00:09:50,550 --> 00:09:51,390
This is complicated.

218
00:09:51,670 --> 00:09:52,510
Be careful.

219
00:09:52,790 --> 00:09:53,630
Get out ASAP.

220
00:09:59,080 --> 00:10:00,630
Where's Lin Zhi'er? Where did she go?

221
00:10:01,510 --> 00:10:02,350
I'm right here.

222
00:10:02,910 --> 00:10:04,320
Mom's about to faint. Get her meds.

223
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:05,840
Okay.

224
00:10:10,636 --> 00:10:12,142
Has Fei Yifan been giving you trouble?

225
00:10:13,790 --> 00:10:14,630
Fei Yifan?

226
00:10:23,670 --> 00:10:25,240
(Why does she seem so different?)

227
00:10:35,750 --> 00:10:37,030
(What on earth is going on?)

228
00:10:38,870 --> 00:10:39,790
(Am I seeing things?)

229
00:10:53,820 --> 00:10:57,660
(Lu Tingyu's wife, Lin Zhi'er)

230
00:10:57,670 --> 00:10:58,670
You're finally back.

231
00:11:00,720 --> 00:11:02,240
No, you're the one who's back.

232
00:11:03,320 --> 00:11:04,160
Lin Zhi'er,

233
00:11:05,630 --> 00:11:07,080
why did you fake your disappearance?

234
00:11:07,630 --> 00:11:08,870
And why use me?

235
00:11:10,790 --> 00:11:11,630
You must've felt

236
00:11:11,840 --> 00:11:13,440
how I've lived here

237
00:11:14,670 --> 00:11:16,510
all these years.

238
00:11:17,480 --> 00:11:18,320
Just a decoration.

239
00:11:18,790 --> 00:11:19,750
A punching bag.

240
00:11:20,150 --> 00:11:21,150
A pathetic tool

241
00:11:21,670 --> 00:11:24,510
to keep the two families tied.

242
00:11:26,840 --> 00:11:28,270
As for why I used you,

243
00:11:29,510 --> 00:11:31,030
isn't the answer obvious?

244
00:11:36,240 --> 00:11:37,670
We look exactly alike.

245
00:11:39,030 --> 00:11:40,790
This was my chance to break free

246
00:11:40,910 --> 00:11:41,870
from the cage.

247
00:11:45,240 --> 00:11:46,390
You knew about me long ago?

248
00:11:47,750 --> 00:11:48,840
I saw you once by chance.

249
00:11:50,320 --> 00:11:51,510
I thought it was uncanny,

250
00:11:52,670 --> 00:11:54,120
so I started following you.

251
00:11:55,200 --> 00:11:56,670
I saw you walk into a cafe,

252
00:11:57,750 --> 00:11:59,750
and I sneaked in after you.

253
00:12:00,440 --> 00:12:03,360
Then I saw your work page,

254
00:12:04,600 --> 00:12:05,670
your case notes,

255
00:12:06,630 --> 00:12:08,550
and your work dashboard.

256
00:12:10,240 --> 00:12:11,080
Then I realized

257
00:12:11,750 --> 00:12:13,870
the girl who looked like me

258
00:12:14,750 --> 00:12:15,790
was actually that capable.

259
00:12:18,720 --> 00:12:21,270
You hired me in secret to look
into the fundraising scheme,

260
00:12:21,790 --> 00:12:22,840
led me to that hotel,

261
00:12:23,600 --> 00:12:25,000
and drew me in step by step?

262
00:12:25,870 --> 00:12:27,910
And I know you're digging it

263
00:12:28,390 --> 00:12:30,000
and you're capable of that.

264
00:12:30,840 --> 00:12:31,680
Don't worry.

265
00:12:31,840 --> 00:12:33,270
I wasn't trying to hurt you.

266
00:12:40,390 --> 00:12:41,360
Oh, my God.

267
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:44,510
We really look exactly alike.

268
00:12:45,960 --> 00:12:46,800
This is insane.

269
00:12:47,030 --> 00:12:49,360
Do you think we could be

270
00:12:50,270 --> 00:12:52,120
like those long-lost sisters
from TV dramas?

271
00:12:56,440 --> 00:12:57,280
What?

272
00:12:57,870 --> 00:12:59,080
Seeing that we look alike,

273
00:12:59,510 --> 00:13:00,910
you want my family fortune now?

274
00:13:01,790 --> 00:13:02,670
No way.

275
00:13:02,750 --> 00:13:04,120
Relax. I'm not interested.

276
00:13:04,480 --> 00:13:05,390
I just think

277
00:13:05,630 --> 00:13:06,720
the fundraising scheme

278
00:13:06,870 --> 00:13:07,910
is about to wrap up.

279
00:13:08,240 --> 00:13:09,630
There's no reason for me to stay.

280
00:13:10,550 --> 00:13:11,790
The fundraising is just a cover.

281
00:13:12,360 --> 00:13:14,320
What's underneath is what matters.

282
00:13:14,960 --> 00:13:16,440
I've been in both families.

283
00:13:17,320 --> 00:13:19,080
I know exactly
what those two dads are like.

284
00:13:20,750 --> 00:13:22,030
The fundraising scheme

285
00:13:22,510 --> 00:13:24,240
must have something bigger behind it.

286
00:13:27,750 --> 00:13:28,960
I hope you won't stop.

287
00:13:30,390 --> 00:13:31,896
Don't you like exposing the dark side?

288
00:13:33,720 --> 00:13:34,960
If there's a hidden secret

289
00:13:35,480 --> 00:13:36,960
behind the project,

290
00:13:37,840 --> 00:13:38,720
I will dig

291
00:13:39,240 --> 00:13:40,240
into it to the end.

292
00:13:40,960 --> 00:13:41,870
Then I'll need you

293
00:13:42,240 --> 00:13:43,480
to stay here

294
00:13:45,120 --> 00:13:45,960
and be me.

295
00:13:49,630 --> 00:13:51,600
(So, she wasn't Lin Zhi'er.)

296
00:13:52,390 --> 00:13:53,230
I'll head off now.

297
00:14:02,320 --> 00:14:03,160
Wen Yan,

298
00:14:03,600 --> 00:14:04,440
thank you.

299
00:14:05,720 --> 00:14:07,150
This is my private encrypted email.

300
00:14:07,360 --> 00:14:08,390
Contact me if you need me.

301
00:14:15,750 --> 00:14:16,590
Take care.

302
00:14:17,150 --> 00:14:17,990
You too.

303
00:14:23,150 --> 00:14:24,000
(Wen Yan...)

304
00:14:24,510 --> 00:14:26,270
(This is getting more interesting.)

305
00:14:26,563 --> 00:14:27,809
Lin Zhi'er, what are you doing?

306
00:14:28,080 --> 00:14:28,920
Come down.

307
00:14:29,960 --> 00:14:31,120
Coming.

308
00:15:19,200 --> 00:15:20,650
♪This door♪

309
00:15:21,050 --> 00:15:25,800
♪Lets in the sky outside♪

310
00:15:26,280 --> 00:15:29,840
♪With a voice even lighter♪

311
00:15:29,840 --> 00:15:32,650
♪Than how you just greeted me♪

312
00:15:33,100 --> 00:15:34,470
♪I know now♪

313
00:15:34,800 --> 00:15:39,680
♪What the chill in my body means♪

314
00:15:40,030 --> 00:15:42,900
♪The moment salt hits the wound♪

315
00:15:43,100 --> 00:15:46,520
♪My heart still beats so naively♪

316
00:15:46,690 --> 00:15:49,680
♪To complete♪

317
00:15:50,140 --> 00:15:53,890
♪A joy that needs no brave pretense♪

318
00:15:54,030 --> 00:15:56,530
♪How cruel sincerity can be♪

319
00:15:56,670 --> 00:16:00,220
♪Like a door with no key♪

320
00:16:00,530 --> 00:16:02,850
♪Maybe you just passed by♪

321
00:16:02,850 --> 00:16:06,430
♪The tears in my eyes♪

322
00:16:07,140 --> 00:16:09,690
♪You looked like you had nothing to say♪

323
00:16:09,690 --> 00:16:11,430
♪Then got so good at being cold♪

324
00:16:11,430 --> 00:16:14,270
♪That's why a smile feels so precious♪

325
00:16:14,480 --> 00:16:16,570
♪Maybe you just passed by♪

326
00:16:16,720 --> 00:16:21,050
♪The tears burned into my heart♪

327
00:16:21,430 --> 00:16:23,720
♪Let's say silence was just for show♪

328
00:16:23,720 --> 00:16:28,390
♪Even if I've grown another year♪
